ALLEN v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 26,

September Term, 1965.]

Decided October 22, 1965. Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Horney, Marbury and Barnes, JJ. Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Sklar in the court below.

Application denied.
